benefits to both merchants and consumers. Merchants can engage directly with a more relevant 

target audience. Consumers can receive offers that align with their preferences and interests. 

● Eliminating Spam: By tokenizing shopping incentives that are tradable for GAT, Merchant 

Tokens will have monetizable value. Whether a consumer “spends” Merchant Tokens to activate 

incentives or not, Merchant Tokens will always be worth something in the hands of the consumer. 

This eliminates the “spam” effect of traditional consumer mass marketing, as each Merchant Token 

can ultimately be traded for GAT. GAT in turn can be traded anywhere in the world for other 

cryptocurrencies such as Bitcoin or Ethereum. 

Value proposition 

The GAT System offers the following benefits to each of its following participants: 

 

Merchants: 

● Micro-target consumers by capturing platform-and-merchant token data and offering coupons or 

points to those that are truly interested in their brands 

● Attract customers to their stores by geolocated A-DropsTM 

 

Users: 

● Offering the ability to exchange points between brands and stores adding liquidity and true value to 

otherwise discarded coupons 

● Receiving more relevant promotions 

● Being able to monetize their points and coupons which they are not planning on using 

 

Loyalty reward programs: 

● Loyalty points traded to a new user means a new customer acquisition for the company 

● Increase the burn rate of the points to get liabilities off the books while getting them to the hands of 

