● Being able to show customers the value of the points in the form of a token with inherent tradable 

value 

 

Brands: 

● Target customers based on their social profiles and interests 

● The A-DropTM technology gives merchants the ability to airdrop promotions to new customers, 

which for instance have held and used the brands’ tokens in the past users and merchants will also 

